df.rename(columns={"participant.code": "participant", "participant.label": "participant_label", "group.id_in_subsession": "group_id", 
                   "session.code": "session"}, inplace=True)
df.rename(columns={c: c.replace("player.", "") for c in df.columns}, inplace=True) 
df.rename(columns={c: c.replace("group.", "") for c in df.columns}, inplace=True) 
df.rename(columns={c: c.replace("subsession.", "") for c in df.columns}, inplace=True) 

df.loc[:, "group_uid"] = df.apply(lambda row: f"{row.session[:4]}g{row.group_id}", axis=1)

fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(12, 6))

sns.lineplot(data=df, x="round_number", y="public_account", hue="treatment", hue_order=["tax_subvention", "injunctif_global", "injunctif_local", "engagement"], 
             marker=".", style="treatment", ci=None, lw=2, ax=ax)
ax.set(ylabel="Investissement", xlabel="Périodes", xticks=df.round_number.unique(), ylim=(0, 20))
ax.legend(handles=ax.get_legend().legendHandles, labels=["Taxe / Subvention", "Norme Sociale Globale", "Norme Sociale Locale", "Engagement Personnel"], 
          ncol=4, loc="upper center")
ax.axvline(x=4.5, ymin=0, ymax=17.5/20, ls="--", color="gray")
ax.axvline(x=8.5, ymin=0, ymax=17.5/20, ls="--", color="gray")
ax.text(x=2.5, y=16.5, s="Jeu initial", ha="center")
ax.text(x=6.5, y=16.5, s="Levier", ha="center")
ax.text(x=10.5, y=16.5, s="Retour au jeu initial", ha="center")

fig.tight_layout()

Evolution par groupe pour chaque levier¶

In [91]:
fig, ax = plt.subplots(2, 2, figsize=(12, 12), sharex=True, sharey=True)
ax = ax.flatten()

for i, e in enumerate(["tax_subvention", "injunctif_global", "injunctif_local", "engagement"]): 
    sns.lineplot(data=df.loc[df.treatment == e], x="round_number", y="public_account", hue="group_uid", marker=".", style="group_uid", legend=False, ci=None, 
                 ax=ax[i])
    ax[i].set(ylabel="Investissement", xlabel="Périodes", xticks=df.round_number.unique(), ylim=(0, 20), 
              title=["Taxe / Subvention", "Norme Sociale Globale", "Norme Sociale Locale", "Engagement Personnel"][i])
    if e == "injunctif_global":
        normglob = df.loc[(df.treatment == e) & (df.round_number == 5)].social_norm_global.iloc[0]
        ax[i].axhline(y=normglob, color="black")
        ax[i].text(x=6.5, y=15.5, s=f"Norme atelier : {normglob}", ha="center")
    ax[i].axvline(x=4.5, ymin=0, ymax=17.5/20, ls="--", color="gray")
    ax[i].axvline(x=8.5, ymin=0, ymax=17.5/20, ls="--", color="gray")
    ax[i].text(x=2.5, y=16.5, s="Jeu initial", ha="center")
    ax[i].text(x=6.5, y=16.5, s="Levier", ha="center")
    ax[i].text(x=10.5, y=16.5, s="Retour au jeu initial", ha="center")

fig.suptitle("Evolution par groupe pour chaque levier")
fig.tight_layout()
